highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “All Too Well (10 Minute Version) (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” is the highest at #1.
“All Too Well (10 Minute Version) (Taylor's Version) (From The Vault)” by Taylor Swift is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #1.
“Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 250 weeks straight.
“Enchanted” by Taylor Swift is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 93 spots at #61.
